definition: Pisces (star sign)
surname Shuang
two/double/pair/both/even (number)
surname Yu
fish/CL:條|条[tiao2],尾[wei3]
Pisces (constellation and sign of the zodiac)

sentences.english: The two fish of Pisces show Christianity's split between spirit and matter.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼宫的两条鱼表明基督教的灵性与物质的分离。

sentences.english: These are some of the basic compatibility traits between Capricorn and Pisces zodiac signs.
sentences.chinese: 这些事摩羯和双鱼配对的基本特征。

sentences.english: Pisces will generally not mind if the Aries wants to be the boss.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼通常不会在意白羊是否想成为老板。

sentences.english: Pictured above, the gegenschein is seen superposed toward the constellation of Pisces.
sentences.chinese: 如图所示，与双鱼座方向重叠的位置可以看到对日照。

sentences.english: Piscean tends to be generally good-natured and very kind and loving.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼座更倾向于和蔼，友好而钟情。

sentences.english: I am pisces, my surname is Lin(forest in chinese) testified that everyone says I am patient and water.
sentences.chinese: 我是双鱼座，我又姓林，大家都说我和水很有缘。

sentences.english: Single fish will find their red fish or bae fish this year.
sentences.chinese: 单身双鱼座今年会找到他们的红鱼或者爱鱼。

sentences.english: Your Pisces friend is a sucker for romance.
sentences.chinese: 你的双鱼是一个浪漫主义者。

sentences.english: Pisces is ruled by the planet Neptune.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼的守护星是海王星。

sentences.english: Pisces is a constellation south of Andromeda.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼座位于仙女座的南边。

sentences.english: Pisces lies between Aries and Aquarius in the northern skies.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼位于北方天空中白羊座和宝瓶座之间。

sentences.english: The Twelfth Sign of the Zodiac which rules the Twelfth House, the House of Everything that has gone before.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼是黄道的第十二个星座，统治第十二宫。

sentences.english: The adage 'opposites attract', holds true when you think of Virgo and Pisces compatibility.
sentences.chinese: “异性相吸”很好的形容了处女座和双鱼座间的关系。

sentences.english: Your sign is one of the busiest during the next six weeks.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼座在今后的六周是最忙的星座之一。

sentences.english: Pisces skips the whole thing to compose poetry to the Moon.
sentences.chinese: 双鱼座干脆跳过步骤，直接对月吟诗去了。

sentences.english: You are about to become quite a force of nature, dear Pisces.
sentences.chinese: 你将会具有很强的影响力，亲爱的双鱼。
